---
template_id: "6fd910fd-120c-4e58-9ef3-15ffc5bd6edc"
template_name: triage_vaccination_will_happen_mmr_second_dose
subject: "<%= short_patient_name %> needs another dose of the <%= programme_name_for_parents(mmr_programme.variant_for(patient:)) %> vaccination"
---
<% variant = mmr_programme.variant_for(patient:) -%>
<% previous_dose = patient_previous_dose_label(patient, mmr_programme, academic_year) -%>
<% next_dose = patient_next_dose_label(patient, mmr_programme, academic_year) -%>
We recently gave <%= short_patient_name %> their <%= previous_dose %> dose of the <%= programme_name_for_parents(variant) %> vaccination. To be fully vaccinated, they need <%= mmr_programme.maximum_dose_sequence %> doses.

We’re coming to <%= location_name %> on <%= next_session_dates %> and plan to give <%= short_patient_name %> their <%= next_dose %> dose then. Please let them know about this.

If <%= short_patient_name_apos %> health changes, or you arrange for them to get their <%= next_dose %> dose somewhere else, contact us. You can email <%= subteam_email %> or phone <%= subteam_phone %>.
